languages.text: "Все слишком суетятся. Да, и ты тоже. А я — я думаю о вечном".
"People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."
languages.original_text: "Все слишком суетятся. Да, и ты тоже. А я — я думаю о вечном".

traits.locale_text: "People fuss too much. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

languages.text: “人们太在乎那些并不重要的东西了。没错，你也是这样，但我不是，我已经开悟了。”
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

traits.locale_text: “人们太在乎那些并不重要的东西了。没错，你也是这样，但我不是，我已经开悟了。”

languages.text: «La gente se preocupa demasiado por cosas irrelevantes. Sí, tú también. Pero yo no. Yo trasciendo».
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

traits.locale_text: «La gente se preocupa demasiado por cosas irrelevantes. Sí, tú también. Pero yo no. Yo trasciendo».

languages.text: 「人ってのはどうでもいいことを気にしすぎる。そう、あんたもだ。でも、俺は違う――俺はそういうのを超越してんだ」
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

traits.locale_text: 「人ってのはどうでもいいことを気にしすぎる。そう、あんたもだ。でも、俺は違う――俺はそういうのを超越してんだ」

languages.text: "Den Leuten liegt viel zu viel an unbedeutenden Dingen. Ja, das gilt auch für Euch. Für mich jedoch nicht – ich stehe über den Dingen."
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

traits.locale_text: "Den Leuten liegt viel zu viel an unbedeutenden Dingen. Ja, das gilt auch für Euch. Für mich jedoch nicht – ich stehe über den Dingen."

languages.text: « Les gens s'attachent trop à des choses qui n'ont aucune importance. Oui, vous aussi. Mais pas moi. Moi, j'ai évolué. »
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

languages.text: "Millet eften püften şeylere çok kafayı takıyor. Evet, sen de sen de. Ama ben öyle miyim ya, ben erdim."
languages.original_text: "People care too much about things that don't matter. Yes, you do too. Not me, though — I transcend."

traits.locale_text: "İnsanlar önemi olmayan şeyleri fazla umursuyor. Evet, sen de umursuyorsun. Ben umursamıyorum, ben erdim."
